<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title><%= @settings.github.org.capitalize %> Github Feed Fetcher</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Github Feed Fetcher</h1>
    <h2>For <%= @settings.github.org.capitalize %></h2>
    <p>Results are pushed every ten minutes to
      <a href="https://gist.github.com/<%= @settings.github.gist %>">
        this gist</a>.</p>
    <p>Access the raw JSON
      <a href="https://raw.github.com/gist/<%= @settings.github.gist %>/feed.json">
        straight from Github</a>.</p>
    <p>Here's a
      <a href="/pretty">slightly prettier version</a>.</p>
    <p><small>Coded by
      <a href="http://passcod.net">passcod</a>,
      code available
      <a href="https://github.com/ualug/github-feed">here</a>.
      <br/>
      This HTML you're reading is not so great, sorry.
      <br/>
      And CSS free!
    </small></p>
  </body>
</html>
